لَآءِ شَهِيدًۭا","translation":"How, then, [will the sinners fare on Judgment Day,] when We shall bring forward witnesses from within every community, and bring thee [O Prophet] as witness against them?","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/534.mp3","surahId":4,"words":[{"id":42009,"position":1,"arabic":"فَكَيْفَ","translation":"কেমন অতঃপর (হবে)","audioUrl":"wbw/004_041_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42010,"position":2,"arabic":"إِذَا","translation":"যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/004_041_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42011,"position":3,"arabic":"جِئْنَا","translation":"আমরা হাজির করব","audioUrl":"wbw/004_041_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42012,"position":4,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"মধ্য হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_041_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42013,"position":5,"arabic":"كُلِّ","translation":"প্রত্যেক","audioUrl":"wbw/004_041_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42014,"position":6,"arabic":"أُمَّةٍۭ","translation":"উম্মতের","audioUrl":"wbw/004_041_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42015,"position":7,"arabic":"بِشَهِيدٍۢ","translation":"একজন সাক্ষী","audioUrl":"wbw/004_041_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42016,"position":8,"arabic":"وَجِئْنَا","translation":"এবং আমরা হাজির করব","audioUrl":"wbw/004_041_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42017,"position":9,"arabic":"بِكَ","translation":"তোমাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_041_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42018,"position":10,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/004_041_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42019,"position":11,"arabic":"هَـٰٓؤُلَآءِ","translation":"তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/004_041_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42020,"position":12,"arabic":"شَهِيدًۭا","translation":"সাক্ষী হিসেবে","audioUrl":"wbw/004_041_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42021,"position":13,"arabic":"٤١","translation":"(৪১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":42,"arabic":"يَوْمَئِذٍۢ يَوَدُّ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا۟ وَعَصَوُا۟ ٱلرّ